data.description: Looky Looky Looky!!! This home has an assumable loan at 2.375%. There's a lot of room to move around in this home boasting 4 bedrooms, large living , dinning room and 2 baths. Plenty of outdoor space to relax and/or entertain. Ready for a full garden. All the rooms in the home are huge. Newer appliances, granite counter tops, two car garage. Fireplace for added warmth during the winter months. MWC schools. Located down from Tinker Air Force Base, shopping, highways, many restaurants, medical, dental and entertainment (Movie theaters/bowling etc). THERE IS A $3,000 CARPET ALLOWANCE OR YOU COULD USE THAT TOWARDS YOUR CLOSING COST. New AC Compressor to be paid at closing. THIS HOME IS OCCUPIED PLEASE DO NOT GO TO THE HOME UNLESS YOU HAVE AN APPT.
